data.description: Adorable freshly remodeled brick ranch home on large corner lot. Home has had many updates recently with new kitchen, flooring throughout, bathrooms updated. Open concept living, dining, and kitchen areas. Electric fireplace insert on wooden accent wall for ambiance lighting as well. Sun porch with skylights and hot tub. Large oversized garage and also a 10x12 shed with loft.
